    2. Even though I "co-coded" this JS file with the video 4-5 times, my application still doesn't actually generate a password.  There must be some bug in the JS file that was born when I was coding along with the video.

## Thoughts for Future Development and Feedback Request

Thoughts on Future Development:

I am constantly needing to generate new passwords for applications at work, and thought this application might be useful for those needs.  Additional features I might add are:
    1. the ability to use the application offline or outside of a web browser.
    2. the  ability store used passwords in a seperate location or sister application.
    3. other security features.


